Prof Caslib once said:

"You know class Wittgenstein is very handsome.. kaya nga sya bakla. and he was also Hitlers' classmate my photo nga sila e.... as we all know.. one turned out to be gay... the other a monster"

Eng1 class, UPD. Tinanong ni Sir kung ano ang isang magandang babae sa perspective ng isang Pilipino.

We said "fair skinned", he wrote "fair skinned" on the board;
we said "tall", he wrote "tall";
we said "with shiny hair", he wrote "shiny hair";
we said "rich", he wrote "rich" ...

We said "smart" ...

he wrote "UP". :)

